flowchart TD
  START([enqueue / schedule]) --> CREATE[create job · compute checksum]
  CREATE --> IDEM{idempotencyKey completed?}
  IDEM -->|yes| SHORT[return completed job\nrecord duplicate]
  IDEM -->|no| DEDUP{dedupKey live?}
  DEDUP -->|yes| DUP[return existing\nrecord duplicate]
  DEDUP -->|no| PERSIST[persist · JobQueued]

  PERSIST --> MODE{enqueue or schedule?}
  MODE -->|schedule| SCH[status = scheduled]
  MODE -->|enqueue| QUEUED[status = queued]
  SCH --> WAIT[(await tick when due)]
  QUEUED --> WAIT

  WAIT --> ORDER[tick: order due jobs\npriority desc, then FIFO seq]
  ORDER --> RUN[status = running · attempt++ · JobStarted]
  RUN --> HANDLER[await handler payload, ctx]

  HANDLER --> OK{resolved?}
  OK -->|yes| TMO{exceeded timeout?}
  TMO -->|no| DONE[status = completed\nrecord latency · JobCompleted]
  TMO -->|yes| FAIL
  OK -->|threw| FAIL[failure]

  FAIL --> RETRY{retryPolicy.shouldRetry?}
  RETRY -->|yes| RESCH[status = retrying\nnextAttemptAt = now + backoff\nJobFailed willRetry · JobRetried]
  RETRY -->|no| DL[status = dead_letter\nJobFailed deadLettered]
  RESCH --> WAIT

  DONE --> END([terminal])
  DL --> END

  RECOVER[[recovery pass:\nrunning past timeout → failure]] -.-> FAIL
